name: The Bearer
description:
A figure emerges from the sea. 
I am dazzled and everything is flooded with a warm colour - red.
 The water brushes against his scaly skin. The Mediterranean sea drips from his dreadlocks.The light bearer smiles at those around him. 
He illuminates and guides them in his sonorous silence.
Max, the light bearer

Pentax Me-Super
Summer 2021
Home developed-Ultramax 400 +1 Step
